<p class="title">Seeing REDD: Science, Policy and Politics in Biodiversity and Climate Change.</p>
<p class="title">Peter Bridgewater, Chair JNCC</p>
<p class="title">14th April 2011, 6.00pm.  The Linnean Society</p>

